<note n="0689005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0689005">今莫作＝念莫住【聖】</note>
<note n="0689006" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0689006">無禪無智＝無智無禪【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0690001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0690001">示＝亦【聖】</note>
<note n="0690002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0690002">為＋（名）【聖】</note>
<note n="0690003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0690003">薩＝問【宮】</note>
<note n="0690004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0690004">則＝即【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0690005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0690005">亦＝示【三】【宮】【聖】</note>
<note n="0690006" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0690006">求＝於【三】【宮】，來【聖】</note>
<note n="0690007" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0690007">〔佛〕－【聖】</note>
<note n="0690008" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0690008">唯＝惟【宮】＊</note>
<note n="0690009" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0690009">染＝深【聖】＊</note>
<note n="0690010" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0690010">夫＝失【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0691001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0691001">瓔＝纓【聖】</note>
<note n="0691002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0691002">踊＝涌【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0691003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0691003">光明皇后願文【聖】</note>
</p>
